Package myVelibGUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddUserTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of adding a new user to a network.
    ClientApplication
    The Client Application class is the frame of the GUI, it is composed of various components which enables to create commands.
    DisplayTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of displaying the status of a network.
    Map  
    OfflineOnlineTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of setting a station online/offline.
    PlanningTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of planning a ride for a given user.
    RentBikeTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of renting a bike at a given station.
    ReturnBikeTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of returning a bike at a given station.
    ReturnPlanBikeTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of returning a bike at the station calculated by the ride plan maker.
    SetupTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of creating a new network.
    SortTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of sorting stations of a given network.
    StatisticsTab
    Tab that provides the application with the possibility of displaying the statistics of a given station and of a given user.
